<div class="sect4">
<h5 id="managing_sasl_encryption_and_authentication">Managing SASL Encryption and Authentication</h5>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Dispatch Router supports SASL for authentication and payload encryption. The following table lists the common <code>qdmanage</code> commands you can use to secure incoming and outgoing connections for a router in your router network.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>For more information about the attributes you can use with these commands, see the <a href="#router_configuration_file_router">router</a> and <a href="#router_configuration_file_listener">listener</a> sections in the <em>Configuration Reference</em>.</p>
</div>
<div class="admonitionblock note">
<table>
<tr>
<td class="icon">
<div class="title">Note</div>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="paragraph">
